
##############################################
    REST : Representational State Transfer
##############################################

LightWeight Approach for communication between applications

Rest is language independent:

The Client application can use ANY Programming language
The Server application can use ANY programming language

RestFul App can use any Data format.
I like using JSON.

Rest calls can be made over HTTP, Rest is language independent.



REST over HTTP

Leverage HTTP methods for CRUD operations.

    HTTP METHOD    ||   CRUD Operation
    _________________________________________
    POST           ||   Create a new entity
    GET            ||   Read a list of entities or single entity
    PUT            ||   Update an existing entity


#######################
  HTTP Request Message
#######################
Has 3 main parts:

- Request Line
- Header Variables
- Message Body

      Request Line:    The HTTP Command
            Has the POST,GET or PUT command.

      Header Variables:  Request metadata
            Has addition information about the request

      Message body: contents of the message.


#######################
  HTTP Response Message
#######################
Has 3 main parts:

- Response Line
- Header Variables
- Message Body

      Response Line : server protocol and status code
          could be one of the http status code: 200,404,500

      Header variables: response metadata
          information about the data, content type: xml or json, size etc.

      Message body: contents of message
           The data that is being sent.


MIME Content Types:
The message format is described by MIME content type.
    Multipurpose Internet Mail-Extension.

Syntax:   type/sub-type

Example:   text/html , text/plain
          application/json ,,application/xml

